<topic id='element_start_date__hospital_provider_spell_.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: START DATE (HOSPITAL PROVIDER SPELL) - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_start_date__hospital_provider_spell_">START DATE (HOSPITAL PROVIDER SPELL)</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_activity_date">ACTIVITY DATE</xref>
 where the 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_activity_date_type">ACTIVITY DATE TYPE</xref>
 is National Code 
              <i>'<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                  keyref="business_definition_start_date">Start Date</xref>'</i>
 of the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_hospital_provider_spell">Hospital Provider Spell</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_start_date">Start Date</xref>
 of the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_hospital_provider_spell">Hospital Provider Spell</xref>
 is the date of admission: the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_consultant">CONSULTANT</xref>
 or 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_midwife">MIDWIFE</xref>
 has assumed responsibility for care following the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_decision_to_admit">DECISION TO ADMIT</xref>
 the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_start_date__hospital_provider_spell_">START DATE (HOSPITAL PROVIDER SPELL)</xref>
 is used by the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_secondary_uses_service">Secondary Uses Service</xref>
 to derive the 
              <b>
            <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                  keyref="supporting_definition_healthcare_resource_group">Healthcare Resource Group</xref>
         </b>
  
              <b>4</b>. Failure to correctly populate this data element is likely to result in an incorrect 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_healthcare_resource_group">Healthcare Resource Group</xref>, usually associated with lower levels of healthcare resource.        </p>
      <p>
For further information, please refer to the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/services/secondary-uses-service-sus/payment-by-results-guidance"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Payment by Results Guidance</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
